*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM APPEND_LOG USING FP_STAT FP_TYPE FP_TEXT.
  CLEAR: GT_LOG.
  GT_LOG-STAT = FP_STAT.
  GT_LOG-TYPE = FP_TYPE.
  GT_LOG-TEXT = FP_TEXT.
